      "duration": 1.91,
      "size": 30528,
      "text": "有没有一种密码，无论敌人多聪明，都绝对无法破译？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "one-time-pad",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/one-time-pad/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.83,
      "size": 29232,
      "text": "答案是有的，它叫一次一密，理论上完美保密。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "one-time-pad",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/one-time-pad/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "它的秘密，藏在一个最简单的运算里，异或。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "one-time-pad",
      "section_id": "xor",
      "line_id": "xor-1",
      "filename": "xor-xor-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/one-time-pad/yunxi/xor-xor-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.91,
      "size": 30528,
      "text": "把明文和密钥的每一位逐个做异或，就得到密文。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "one-time-pad",
      "section_id": "xor",
      "line_id": "xor-3",
      "filename": "xor-xor-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/one-time-pad/yunxi/xor-xor-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "所以拿密文再异或同一把密钥，明文就原封不动地回来了。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "one-time-pad",
      "section_id": "key",
      "line_id": "key-1",
      "filename": "key-key-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/one-time-pad/yunxi/key-key-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.61,
      "size": 25776,
      "text": "密钥必须是真随机的，而且和明文一样长。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "one-time-pad",
      "section_id": "key",
      "line_id": "key-2",
      "filename": "key-key-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/one-time-pad/yunxi/key-key-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "每一位密钥都是抛硬币般的零或一，毫无规律可循。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "one-time-pad",
      "section_id": "perfect",
      "line_id": "per-2",
      "filename": "perfect-per-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/one-time-pad/yunxi/perfect-per-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "既然每种明文都可能，密文就没有泄露任何信息，这就是完美保密。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "one-time-pad",
      "section_id": "perfect",
      "line_id": "per-3",
      "filename": "perfect-per-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/one-time-pad/yunxi/perfect-per-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.49,
      "size": 39888,
      "text": "但密钥绝不能重用，两条密文一异或，密钥抵消，明文关系就暴露了。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "one-time-pad",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/one-time-pad/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
